        {
          "alignItems": "center",
          "children": [
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "content": "4",
                      "fill": "#94A3B8",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "fNUTt",
                      "name": "lpHead",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "THE LAST FRONTIER",
                      "fill": "#94A3B8",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 9,
                      "fontWeight": "600",
                      "id": "R0hN7",
                      "letterSpacing": 2,
                      "name": "lpChap",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "fill": "#CBD5E1",
                      "height": 1,
                      "id": "rFlfs",
                      "name": "lpLine",
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "width": 40
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "The colony's distress beacon had been broadcasting for eleven days before anyone on Aria detected it. Not because the signal was weak — it wasn't — but because it used an encryption protocol that hadn't been standard since the founding era. Dr. Zhang was the one who recognized it.",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "XriZe",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "name": "lpPara1",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "\"This is old,\" she'd said, fingers tracing the waveform on her display. \"Really old. Pre-settlement old.\" The implication hung between them like smoke: something had been calling for help from Kepler-9 long before humans had arrived.",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "MTzCC",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "name": "lpPara2",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    }
                  ],
                  "effect": {
                    "blur": 12,
                    "color": "#00000030",
                    "offset": {
                      "x": 0,
                      "y": 2
                    },
                    "shadowType": "outer",
                    "type": "shadow"
                  },
                  "fill": "#FFFDF9",
                  "gap": 20,
                  "height": 680,
                  "id": "VLnd2",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "name": "Left Page",
                  "padding": [
                    40,
                    48
                  ],
                  "type": "frame",
                  "width": 500,
                  "x": 20,
                  "y": 20
                }
              ],
              "height": 720,
              "id": "6BDed",
              "layout": "none",
              "name": "Left Page Bleed",
              "stroke": {
                "fill": "#EF444440",
                "thickness": 1
              },
              "type": "frame",
              "width": 540
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "content": "5",
                      "fill": "#94A3B8",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 10,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "pNKPx",
                      "name": "rpHead",
                      "textAlign": "right",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "Marcus took the datapad without a word. The numbers confirmed what Elena's expression had already told him: the colony's atmospheric processors were failing faster than projected. At current rates, Kepler-9's breathable zones would shrink by forty percent within eighteen months.",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "FaRKi",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "name": "rpPara1",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "\"Options?\" he asked, though he already knew the answer would be insufficient.",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "1HdNR",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "name": "rpPara2",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "\"Three.\" Elena held up fingers as she spoke. \"First, we accelerate the terraforming schedule — but that requires resources we don't have. Second, we evacuate the outer settlements and consolidate — which means abandoning two thousand people's homes. Third...\" She paused.",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "BEQNT",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "name": "rpPara3",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "\"Third?\"",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "cTAbA",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "name": "rpPara4",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "content": "\"We ask Kai for help.\"",
                      "fill": "#334155",
                      "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "id": "1lZPU",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "name": "rpPara5",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "type": "text",
                      "width": "fill_container"
                    }
                  ],
                  "effect": {
                    "blur": 12,
                    "color": "#00000030",
                    "offset": {
                      "x": 0,
                      "y": 2
                    },
                    "shadowType": "outer",
                    "type": "shadow"
                  },
                  "fill": "#FFFDF9",
                  "gap": 20,
                  "height": 680,
                  "id": "WPmMh",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "name": "Right Page",
                  "padding": [
                    40,
                    48
                  ],
                  "type": "frame",
                  "width": 500,
                  "x": 20,
                  "y": 20
                }
              ],
              "height": 720,
              "id": "w01v0",
